 and new set is generated based on need.

The Buddhists do not believe in t=
he existence of a soul. They believe in Shunya - which is similar to our id=
ea of Atmah. Therefore their idea of reincarnation is very different. It is=
 like an energy stream made up of mind, body that coalesces together to giv=
e the impression of an individual being, which upon death get disintegrated=
